  GAME INFORMATION:
 -------------------
 
  Create and manage your own successful farm with John Deere American Farmer.
  You'll decide what crops to plant, livestock to raise, employees to hire,
  equipment to purchase and structures to build. Plagues, weather, market
  trends, employee skill level and much more will play a role as you make
  decisions that will determine the ultimate success of your farm.
 
 
  GAME FEATURES:
 ----------------
 
  * Plant crops, keep livestock and build structures while responding to
    unexpected events and changing seasons.
 
  * Purchase and control authentic John Deere branded equipment -- tractors,
    combines, planters, cultivators and more.
 
  * Ten diverse scenarios, each with three levels of difficulty.
 
  * Overcome infestations, unpredictable weather and disgruntled employees.
 
  * Use the built-in Map Editor to create your own unique scenarios.
 
 
  INSTALLATION INFORMATION:
 ---------------------------
 
  Extract, burn, install. Copy our crack from the CRACK directory on your CD,
  overwriting the original exe. Enjoy!
